title: Can The Bert Show Guess These El Salvadoran Slang Words?
description:
Have you ever thought about what slang words sound like in other countries? 
Our Assistant Producer, Just Romeo, is from El Salvador. For fun, he brought some El Salvadorian slang words to the studio, and based on what they sounded like the other members of The Bert Show guess what they mean.
